<BaseLayout title="SharedID — First-Party Identity & Privacy Platform (Prebid)">
  <article>
    <h1>SharedID — Identity & Privacy (Prebid)</h1>

    <p><strong>Role:</strong> Principal Technical Product Manager (Platform & Ecosystem)</p>
    <p><strong>Public Ecosystem:</strong> Prebid.org (Open Source)</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Problem</h2>
      <p>
        Industry-wide changes—including browser privacy controls and third-party cookie deprecation—required a new approach to identity that preserved addressability while respecting privacy regulations. Publishers needed a scalable, compliant solution to act as first-party addressers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Context & Constraints</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>GDPR and global privacy compliance</li>
        <li>Industry adoption required trust, neutrality, and transparency</li>
        <li>Technical limitations of third-party cookies</li>  
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Approach</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Designed a first-party identity solution intended for industry-wide adoption</li>
        <li>Proactively identified and mitigated regulatory, technical, and adoption risks</li>
        <li>Leveraged Prebid and IAB Tech Lab participation to drive ecosystem consensus</li>  
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Execution</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Led delivery with a focused product and engineering team</li>
        <li>Donated the solution to Prebid, leveraging its Global Vendor List (GVL) for GDPR compliance</li>
        <li>Removed third-party cookie dependency, shifting to per-publisher UUIDs</li>
        <li>Collaborated with <strong>Prebid</strong> and the <strong>IAB Tech Lab</strong> to define standardized identifier transport via the OpenRTB Extended ID framework</li>  
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Impact</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Adopted across 50%+ of browser-based ad requests in the open web ecosystem</li>
        <li>Demonstrated measurable CPM lift when present</li>
        <li>Established industry-aligned, privacy-forward identity infrastructure</li>
        <li>EBecame foundational to sell-side identity and audience strategy</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
